<%- include("partials/header") %>
<main>
    <section>
        <article>
            <%= user.email %>
            <form action="/logout" method="post">
                <button type="submit">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </article>
    </section>
    <img src="https://github.com/RMA1040/ProjectWebOntwikkeling2RMA/blob/main/public/images/IRC-index.png?raw=true" alt="IRC headliner" height="100%" width="100%">
    <section>
        <h1>Intercontinental Racing Championship</h1>
        <p>
            The Intercontinental Racing Championship (IRC) is the pinnacle of global motorsport competition, uniting elite drivers and world-renowned teams from every corner of the planet. Established to push the limits of speed, skill, and strategy, the IRC is more than just a racing series — it's a showcase of human ambition and engineering excellence.
            With circuits spanning multiple continents and climates, the IRC challenges competitors across a diverse range of conditions — from high-speed street races in iconic cities to technically demanding grand prix circuits. The championship celebrates both veteran legends and rising stars, making it a battleground where experience meets raw talent.
            At the heart of the IRC lies a commitment to innovation, fierce competition, and international unity through sport. Each race is a high-stakes spectacle of precision, adrenaline, and passion — earning the IRC its place as the world’s premier motorsport league.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section class="grid">
        <a href="/drivers">
            <article>
                <h3>Drivers</h3>
                <p>Total Drivers: <%= drivers.length %></p>
                <p>Active Drivers: <%= drivers.filter(d => d.isActive).length %></p>
            </article>
        </a>
        <a href="/teams">
            <article>
                <h3>Teams</h3>
                <p>Total Teams: <%= teams.length %></p>
                <p>Total Championships: <%= teams.reduce((sum, team) => sum + team.amountOfChampionships, 0) %></p>
            </article>
        </a>
    </section>
</main>
<%- include("partials/footer") %>